td.p: A diagram showing an example of the neighbor-joining algorithm applied to 7 taxa. The beginning (completely unresolved), and the ending (completely resolved) trees are shown, and all 3 intermediate steps.
Google doc drawing. Edited drawing also created by me in early 2012.
